Invocation Name: elastic mapreduce flashcards
des:
This skill practices you with Elastic MapReduce(EMR) commands used in cloud computing. It helps you to get familiarize with the commands available and also to know the details of each commands so that you can store/remember to check the place to know further about EMR commands. 

Alexa can help you learn EMR commands. You can review the flash cards and then test your knowledge. At any point you can say "Alexa, review mode" to switch to review or say "Alexa, test mode" to start a test. You can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next card. At any point during the test, you can say "Alexa, what's my score" to get your current test score. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
